  <brief_title>Proof of Concept Study of Gevokizumab in the Treatment of Pyoderma Gangrenosum</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label, Proof of Concept Study of Gevokizumab in the Treatment of the Acute, Inflammatory Phase of Pyoderma Gangrenosum</official_title>
